  <title>lame-&lame-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The LAME package contains an MP3 encoder and optionally, an MP3 frame
      analyzer. This is useful for creating and analyzing compressed audio
      files.
    </para>

